long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension helps you search for profitable items from Counter-Strike (CS:GO & CS2) on the Cs.Money Market. This makes trading easy and convenient!

The extension analyzes the latest items that users have posted on the Cs.Money Market, analyzes their price and compares them with other marketplaces and in case of a favorable price of the item, sends you a notification!
